Authentication in Play! Framework:

 — Basic username/password auth
 — Google openId auth
 — Allow you to add auth means and you both at the same time
 
Usage:

	For the Basic authentication:

annotate the targeted controller with @With(BasicSecurityProvider.class). Extend BasicSecurityExtensionPoint, annotate with @For(BasicSecurityProvider.class), and override methods.

	For the Google authentication:

annotate the targeted controller with @With(GoogleSecurityProvider.class). Extend GoogleSecurityExtensionPoint, annotate you class with @For(GoogleSecurityProvider.class), and override methods.


Still in development.

